3. cs.SI (Social and Information Networks): MIMO systems are often used in wireless networks, which fall under the category of social and information networks. 
4. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture): The paper discusses the use of low-density parity-check channel codes, which are commonly used in networking and internet architecture.
